Title: Course Syllabi for Open and Reproducible Methods
Description: A collection of course syllabi from any discipline featuring content to examine or improve open and reproducible research practices.  Email to join project, access articles, or add other syllabi.
Contributors: Richard Ball, Sara Bowman, Garret Christensen, Michael C. Frank, David Funder, Konrad Hinsen, Nicole Janz, Norm Medeiros, Edward Miguel, Brian A. Nosek, Russell Poldrack, Courtney Soderberg, Simine Vazire
Tags: syllabus, research methods, transparency, open science, reproducibility

